description: Location, Location, Location! CITY POINT at its finest.  Studio/1BR unit ready for new owner!  558 SF, open floor plan, central AC, in unit laundry, large closets, freshly painted, stainless steel appliances, quartz counter breakfast bar and storage available.  Full bath offers tile stand up shower and modest vanity/ medicine cabinet.  This unit is a PERFECT opportunity for any Buyer looking to break into the HOT South Boston real estate market.  Located steps from the beach this is possibly one of the most coveted locations in the area!
